ly one word of warning, be afraid... very afraid, whether you have a gun, a bat or a knife the best thing is to flee and NOT fall into madness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You wake up on an idyllic beach, feet in white sand, lulled by a light breeze as the sun sets on the horizon. During this leisurely walk, the gates of hell open to you. Driven by your pride, you think you can cross them without suffering the consequences but quickly the perfect dream in which you found yourself turns into an oppressive nightmare with no way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/13.gif?t=1734650348\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead the fight for your existence in an atmosphere where madness is palpable and anxiety grows with every step you take, face hordes of zombies, solve puzzles or search for the best place to hide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For the bravest among you, prepare to live an extraordinary immersive experience, where horror comes to life and where every moment can seal your fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/20.gif?t=1734650348\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face your inner demons, triumph over your deepest fears. But remember, never, ever succumb to madness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you dare to dive into the endless abyss of Very Bad Dreams?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We will have warned you...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/10.gif?t=1734650348\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["CREATIVE VR3D"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/header.jpg